{"tid":2041662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"後生還後生做運動前都要知道自己有咩條件優勢?","createTime":"2020-05-29T11:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T11:19:37.000Z","uid":195514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c651fb17d8613f218482b29b2cbb611fc4df6f5e","tid":2041662,"uid":195514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"大熱天時由朝到晚 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">體力</span></strong></span>就係分野 <br />\n你估真係個個都可以孭住咁多野係條街罰企成日咩<br />\n但後生就唔同可以輕裝做運動 攰又可以休息再黎過<br />\n睇完新聞 你就知道就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時操到有幾FIT都好 返到屋企個人一咪又係GG<br />\n當每次強度都好高既時候 結果係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道係持久戰都好都要清楚點樣拉長黎做 你估對方真係無限體力無限人手咩 點都會去到一個臨界點 諗諗點樣發揮自身既優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf9c1f014d024573df6da1478990e58b6a8c524","tid":2041662,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"大家記住唔好吸冰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吸左冰嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出嚟曬一陣太耐都會死"},{"pid":"62cd74a7f8804a3a6253bf770e8d1a9fd8ded587","tid":2041662,"uid":195514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33338efeb5d367fd044b821ff42b335dcc67316b","tid":2041662,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"4&times;100同400米邊個跑得快啲<br />\n邊個體能消耗多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa